            <Font size="15.0" />
        </font>
    </Label>
    <Label layoutX="479.0" layoutY="171.0" prefHeight="74.0" prefWidth="486.0" text="1. Boil the mixed vegetables until they are soft, then mash them coarsely.  In a pan, heat some butter or oil. Add the minced garlic and sauté until it's aromatic." wrapText="true">
        <font>
            <Font size="15.0" />
        </font>
    </Label>
    <Label layoutX="479.0" layoutY="245.0" prefHeight="62.0" prefWidth="486.0" text="2. Add the finely chopped onions and green bell pepper. Sauté until they turn soft and translucent." wrapText="true">
