            <Font size="15.0" />
        </font>
    </Label>
    <Label layoutX="479.0" layoutY="301.0" prefHeight="74.0" prefWidth="595.0" text="3. Add the chopped tomatoes and cook until they become mushy and the oil starts to separate.  Add the Pav Bhaji masala, red chili powder, turmeric powder, and salt. Mix well and cook for a couple of minutes." wrapText="true">
