            <Font size="15.0" />
        </font>
    </Label>
    <Label layoutX="478.0" layoutY="378.0" prefHeight="55.0" prefWidth="588.0" text="4. Add the mashed vegetables and mix everything thoroughly. If needed, add some water to achieve your desired consistency." wrapText="true">
