            <Font size="15.0" />
        </font>
    </Label>
    <Label layoutX="478.0" layoutY="493.0" prefHeight="55.0" prefWidth="595.0" text="6. While the bhaji is simmering, split the pav (dinner rolls) into halves and lightly toast them with butter on a griddle." wrapText="true">
