            <Font size="15.0" />
        </font>
    </Label>
    <Label layoutX="479.0" layoutY="552.0" prefHeight="55.0" prefWidth="514.0" text="7. Serve the hot and spicy bhaji with the buttered pav. Garnish with chopped coriander leaves and lemon wedges." wrapText="true">
